  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of Bilastine ophthalmic solution 0.6% compared to vehicle and
      Zaditen (Ketotifen ophthalmic solution 0.025%) for the treatment of the signs and symptoms of
      allergic conjunctivitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
